* (`/workspace/package.json`):\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-ssg-toolkit\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"main\": \"dist/core/index.js\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/ tests/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@types/express\": \"^5.0.6\",\n    \"@types/marked\": \"^5.0.2\",\n    \"express\": \"^5.2.1\",\n    \"marked\": \"^17.0.2\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.1\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.9.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.1.9\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**vitest.config.ts** (`/workspace/vitest.config.ts`):\n```typescript\n- globals: true (use describe/it/expect without imports)\n- testTimeout: 10000ms\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. TypeScript Configuration (`/workspace/tsconfig.json`)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",\n    \"declaration\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*\"]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Key Implementation Notes\n\n1. **Dependency System**: Plugins declare dependencies by name in the `dependencies` array. The engine uses topological sort to ensure correct execution order.\n\n2. **Data Sharing**: `BuildContext.data` is a Map that plugins use to pass data to each other:\n   - `asset-pipeline` → sets `asset-manifest`\n   - `taxonomy` → sets `taxonomy-tags`\n   - `dev-server` → reads from both and sets `dev-server-config`\n\n3. **Plugin Hook Pattern**:\n   - `beforeBuild`: Called once, for setup (e.g., taxonomy building)\n   - `transformContent`: Called for each file (e.g., markdown conversion, URL rewriting)\n   - `afterBuild`: Called once, for finalization (e.g., sitemap/feed generation)\n\n4. **Available Libraries**:\n   - **marked**: For markdown parsing (^17.0.2)\n   - **express**: Type definitions available (^5.0.6)\n   - Both are installed and ready to use\n\n5. **Expected Plugin File Locations**: Each plugin should be in `/workspace/src/plugins/` with name pattern like `markdown-ext.ts`, `asset-pipeline.ts`, etc.\n\n6. **Dependency Order for Plugins**:\n   - `markdown-ext`: No dependencies (converts content)\n   - `asset-pipeline`: After markdown-ext (rewrites URLs)\n   - `syntax-highlight`: After markdown-ext (enhances code blocks)\n   - `taxonomy`: No dependencies (requires files before transforms)\n   - `sitemap`: Depends on `taxonomy` (needs tag pages)\n   - `rss-feed`: Depends on `taxonomy` (needs category data)\n   - `search-index`: No dependencies (reads from ctx.files)\n   - `dev-server`: After all others (reads asset manifest, search index, routes)\n\n---\n\nYou now have **complete details of all 8 plugins** with comprehensive test specifications to implement them!"}],"totalDurationMs":39778,"totalTokens":33987,"totalToolUseCount":19,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":501,"cache_read_input_tokens":30003,"output_tokens":3478,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":501,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[]}}}
